# clasp pushes files inside the rootDir (apps_script/) to the bound Apps Script
# project. This file controls what to skip even inside that directory.
#
# Anything outside apps_script/ is already ignored because of rootDir.
# We keep this file mainly for clarity and future additions.

# Standard junk
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/*.swp
**/*~

# Node / git artefacts (shouldn't be inside apps_script/ but defensive)
**/node_modules/**
**/.git/**

# Documentation we don't want shipped to Apps Script
**/README.md
**/*.test.js
